1. Start Lazarus, go to components/open packaga file(*.lpk)

2. Open lnetpackage-<version>.lpk and compile

3. Go to the "ide" subdirectory and open and install "lnetidepackage.lpk"

4. Let Lazarus restart.

You can learn the basics by using the included examples or from http://wiki.lazarus.freepascal.org/index.php/LNet

Ales Katona